thumb.title: □スパイラル_ - これは愛ですか？ft. 欲音ルコ KIRE 【オリジナル曲】
thumb.description: "Do you really love me?"It's finally here. My 8th song!This song, inspired by Fair Verona's "Downfall of a Well Known Actress", is the last song on my first album "A Rainbow and Beyond" . This song has been produced since December, and it took some time to complete because I was working on other songs at the same time as this song. In fact, some of the other songs have already been completed! Please look forward to it!Translated with DeepL
